ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada - European Union ** Agreement on Transfer and Processing of Passenger Name Record Data **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between Canada and the EUROPEAN UNION on the TRANSFER AND PROCESSING OF PASSENGER NAME RECORD DATA.
